 'In-season soccer S&C session (48h before or after match). A1: Front squat 3x4 @ 80-85% 1RM. B1: Romanian deadlift 3x6. B2: Copenhagen plank 3x15s each side. C1: Single-leg press 3x8. C2: Nordic curl 3x5. D1: Upper body: cable row 2x10. Total: 45 minutes max. Prioritize: quality reps, adequate warm-up, minimal soreness.',
