('Cycling FTP Test (20-Minute Protocol)',
 'cardiovascular', array['quads','glutes','hamstrings'], array['cardiovascular','quads','glutes'],
 'sport_specific', 'cardio', array['bike','power_meter','trainer'], 'advanced', true,
 'Functional Threshold Power test. 10-minute warm-up easy. 5-minute hard effort at 110% estimated FTP. 5-minute recovery easy. 20-minute all-out sustained effort at maximum average power you can hold. Cool down 10 min. FTP = 95% of 20-minute average power. Retest every 6-8 weeks to track fitness.',
