('Cycling Power-Based Training Zones Setup',
 'cardiovascular', array['quads','glutes','hamstrings'], array['cardiovascular','quads','glutes'],
 'sport_specific', 'cardio', array['bike','power_meter'], 'beginner', true,
 'Set up Coggan training zones based on FTP. After FTP test, calculate 7 zones: Z1 Active Recovery: <55% FTP. Z2 Endurance: 56-75%. Z3 Tempo: 76-87%. Z4 Threshold: 88-95%. Z5 VO2max: 106-120%. Z6 Anaerobic: 121-150%. Z7 Neuromuscular: max sprint. Create training week: 3-4 zone 2, 1 threshold, 1 VO2max per week for general amateur.',
 'Using HR alone without power (imprecise due to HR drift); not updating zones after FTP changes; training mostly in zone 3 (grey zone — not aerobic enough, not hard enough); no structure to training weeks.',
