 'Criterium-specific race preparation. Skills to train: (1) Corner entry/exit speed: carry maximum speed through corner. (2) Acceleration from corners: explosive 3-second sprint out of every corner. (3) Positioning: practice moving up in peloton before corners. (4) Attacks: bridge a gap solo. (5) Sprint: position for final sprint from 400m out. Closed circuit practice 6x10-min race simulation.',
