 'Active recovery designed for day-after-hard-session. 30-45 minutes at Zone 1 only: <55% FTP, HR <115 BPM. Spin light gear high cadence 90-100 RPM. No surges, no efforts. Goal: blood flow to clear lactate, psychological refresh, leg flush. If you feel guilty not working harder — that is the point. Optional: add 10 minutes stretching on bike or post-ride.',
