 'Full swim-bike brick. Pool: 1500m (Olympic distance) at race pace — no rest. Exit pool, change, mount bike on trainer or road: 40km at race effort. This tests swim fatigue carrying over to the bike, and practices maintaining power output post-swim. Record: bike power at 5min, 20min, 40min to see how swim affects early bike output.',
