 'Triathlon long run protocol. Effort: Zone 2, conversational (HR 65-75% max). Duration: build from 60 minutes to 120-150 minutes over 12 weeks. Run-walk method for beginners: 4 minutes run / 1 minute walk continuously. Focus: time on feet, aerobic development, run economy. Weekly long run is the most important run session for triathlon.',
