 'Open water specific training. Session in lake or ocean: (1) 400m sighting swim around buoy course. (2) Mass start simulation: 10 swimmers sprint first 50m simultaneously — practice contact tolerance. (3) Drafting: follow another swimmer 1m behind their feet for 500m. (4) Buoy turn practice: left and right tight turns. (5) Full course: 1500m race simulation with sighting and turns.',
