 '21.1km half marathon triathlon run simulation. After 2-hour bike session (90km): T2, start running. Pacing: first 5km at 105-110% goal marathon pace, km 5-15 at goal half marathon race pace, final 6km at or below goal pace. Nutrition: gel every 30-40 minutes, 500ml electrolyte per hour. Mental strategy: break into 5km segments.',
