('Triathlon Mental Performance Training',
 'cardiovascular', array['core','diaphragm'], array['cardiovascular','core'],
 'sport_specific', 'cardio', array['bodyweight'], 'intermediate', false,
 'Psychological skills for triathlon racing. (1) Race visualization: 15-minute guided visualization of perfect race execution daily for race week. (2) Mantras: develop 3 personal mantras for difficult moments. (3) Process focus: identify what is in your control at each moment of the race. (4) Box breathing in training (4-4-4-4) to practice calming under physiological stress. (5) Post-race reflection journaling.',
