 'cardiovascular', array['quads','glutes','core'], array['cardiovascular','quads','glutes'],
 'sport_specific', 'cardio', array['running_shoes','bike','heat_chamber'], 'advanced', true,
 'Adaptation protocols for challenging race environments. Heat: 5-10 day heat acclimatization — train in warmest part of day, extra 500ml fluid daily, reduce intensity by 15%. Altitude: arrive 3+ days before or 10-14 days before (avoid 4-9 day window). Cold water swim: practice in <18°C water 3x per week 4 weeks before cold open water race. Monitor: resting HR, sleep quality, urine colour.',
