 'Triathlon-specific injury prevention program targeting the three most common injuries: (1) IT band syndrome — glute med strengthening, hip drop assessment, VF stretch 3x45s daily. (2) Swimmer''s shoulder — rotator cuff program 3x weekly. (3) Stress fracture prevention — load management, bone density nutrition (calcium + vit D), graded run increases max 10% per week. Track: weekly training load and acute:chronic ratio.',
