 'sport_specific', 'cardio', array['nutrition_products','bottles'], 'intermediate', true,
 'Triathlon race nutrition planning. Sprint (1h): gel at T1 if needed, 500ml water on bike. Olympic (2h): gel every 30-40min starting T1, 1 bottle electrolyte on bike. Half Ironman (4-5h): 60-90g carbs/hour on bike, switch to real food in latter half, cola in last 5km run. Ironman (8-12h): 80-90g carbs/hour, strong sodium intake, test ALL products in long training.',
